        <abstract> 
<p>Hopes WPS may succeed with a new edition of his book [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">13495</hi>]. WPS saw so much more of the natives of Tierra del Fuego than did CD and his opinion of them is probably right.</p> 
            <p>Discourages him from visiting.</p>
